Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,为了重建妖精的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹 哈比 露西开启了寻找同伴之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在蛇姬之鳞 他们找到了温蒂和夏露露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,天空姐妹 雪莉娅和温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是蛇姬之鳞的魔导士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不能跟纳兹你们走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果因为同情才陪伴着我 就不能算是伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚 正义的铁锤将对蛇姬之鳞进行审判
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,血染感谢祭即将开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,居然驱使怪物来袭击我们 蛇鬼也是堕落了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:01:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,燃起来了 我们上 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙比怪物还怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物的数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这些怪物全都冲进玛格丽特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,城市就交给利昂他们保护吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹他们也在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要攻击蛇鬼的中心驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 雪莉娅比露西轻多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 我都想靠自己的力量来保护城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,雪莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,作为敌人相识的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在却在一起守护蛇姬之鳞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为当时和莉娅成为了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是因为温蒂接受了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,灭龙奥义 照破 天空穿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂 你果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不讨厌战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但可以轻易看穿结局的单方面暴力很没有爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你的同情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要手下留情 直到我倒下无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,全部的心意应该用全部的力量来回应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,天之丛云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,天龙的碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我很开心哦 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也觉得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,交个朋友吧 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 雪莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,去会会他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,天空姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,天龙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,天神的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怒号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不过两个小姑娘 有什么费事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 不止两个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,白月飞踢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,夏露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候展示我特训的成果了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,给我找个地方藏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,天龙的翼击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,驱魔师就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,雪莉娅 你冲得太前了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要阻止怪物进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,天神之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这个味道 好像在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,给我等着 哈比小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,开启吧 狮子宫之门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,露西的骑士 参上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,以及 星灵礼服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,狮子座形态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是艾尔莎的魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,换装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很美哦 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在召唤星灵之后 将部分星灵的魔力留在自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 这么一来我也能战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着礼服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是我老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是太可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,冰之 雄鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的 毒爪 百倍毒水母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,波动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,王者冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,王者露西 踢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,踢腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是光属性的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,天龙的钩爪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,天神的北风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,驱魔师在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,雪莉娅 危睑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到我出场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 暂不需要借助您的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小女孩 我有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大 大师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还能飞得起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,地面都被
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得是恶魔心脏的 布鲁诺特·斯特加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的重力之下 无人能动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大师 这么做太过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的魔导士也都被
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不 完全没问题 请随意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,飞吧 飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,雪莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在大师的重力之下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然胆敢偷走哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹 现在不是说这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那个在天狼岛折磨我们的家伙在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁诺特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不记得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要被压扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,火龙的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,碍事 垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是个垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么那张脸我怎么看都不顺眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好强大的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我居然连一步都动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙很危睑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,火焰把地面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,升起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精的尾巴是永存不灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就是妖精的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,别给我擅作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,让这家伙飞起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这一年来 纳兹到底强大了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 做小偷就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,连衣服都烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹 别说教了 快看看周围
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们投降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物全都撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,帮大忙了 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没闹够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经闹得很厉害了 纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是蛇鬼之鳍雇佣了布鲁诺特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁诺特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在才想起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,天狼岛战役后 出现了更了不得的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗 这次轮到我不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿库诺罗利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个你倒是记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我想忘也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 温蒂和雪莉娅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那两人再过个三年 就可以成为我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她们有悄悄话说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想在温蒂面前 表现出自己没问题的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 被纳兹搞得一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那是纳兹呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂果然还是要跟纳兹在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你爱着他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不是那种感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只是仰慕他 把他当成哥哥一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是一种爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是不去的话会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精的尾巴还没有倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为爱着温蒂 爱着妖精的尾巴 才会来到这悝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,顺从内心吧 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就算公会不同 我们也永远都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雪莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,长久以来 受你们照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,保重啊 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要向你们道声谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,夏露露也保重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真不知道该说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我 那么任性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在加入我们之前不就说好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在妖精的尾巴重建之前 暂时加入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,夏露露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原来温蒂和夏露露都没有忘了妖精的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂真是个爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 我会补上天空姐妹的空缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,到我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,婆婆也别胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,重建妖精的尾巴要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,代我向格雷问声好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,话说目前还不知道格雷的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,保重啊 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 雪莉娅也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,已经可以哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我也希望妖精的尾巴能够重建
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你要哭到什么时候 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 妖精的尾巴解散的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,蛇姬的大伙都对我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我又能和纳兹你们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因为同时感到高兴和悲伤而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才刚要开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可是要将所有人都找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 接下来要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里往东走 有个村子 叫雨降村
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一个雨下不停的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,难道那里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,继续踏上寻找伙伴之旅的纳兹一行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在雨降村与落魄居住在此的茱比亚再会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,从她口中听说的格雷的近况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,唤起了纳兹一年前得知的某种不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色的阴影侵蚀着格雷的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,纠缠的黑线将格雷的心灵染上了黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 黑魔术教团
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗公会退散之后 新兴势力的黑色时代已经开始
